Broadmark Overlay Strategy
Broadmark’s Overlay Stategy tactically hedges long equity exposure by shorting index based instruments such as futures and ETFs.

Actively manages portfolio equity exposure with dynamic hedge
Hedge fund investment process with mutual fund liquidity and transparency
Increased diversification with reduction in volatility
Provide tactical risk management by assessing portfolios market risk

























